rom $\\Lambda$CDM at the $1\\sigma$ confidence\nlevel, but agrees with $w=-1$ at the $2\\sigma$ confidence level.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Dec 2011 09:11:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
