ion of CaWO4, ZnWO4, CdWO4,\nPbWO4, GSO(Ce), CeF3, yttrium-aluminum garnet doped with neodymium (YAG:Nd)\ncrystal scintillators were studied. Applicability of these scintillators to\nsearch for double beta decay was discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Dec 2011 15:45:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2011 12:01:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-12-30"}
